reviews.review_text: beautiful recording i am the first to comment on the quality of this recording ?

Awesome AUD I concur, this is a damn good AUD recording. Very punchy and all instruments present, not too much rolling reverb from the room, almost no intrusive crowd noise. This is on a par with the other more famous Jerry Moore recordings like Miami 6-23-74 and the legendary 5-8-77. Somewhat lacking in bottom end, though Phil is still clearly present in the mix.

I Agree Guys. Outstanding Recording !!! I'm right there with yah guys.  Beautiful recording.  I think I've had this show for a while and don't remember why I didn't keep the first set.  But having sed that, I'm throwing four stars at this evening's entertainment for the sound quality and a fun and very collectible second set.
